Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.effects

Class StudentContainer

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.modelObservables.StudentContainerObservable
it.polimi.ingsw.model.effects.StudentContainer
public class StudentContainer extends StudentContainerObservable
StudentContainer contains students that are present on a character. The class is observed by the game in order to automatically insert students on it when a student is picked from it.
